metadata.name: uBox_9/260
metadata.description:
UnitedMake has created a collection of unique e-packages. Located and shipped from around the world, these Mystery e-boxes will contain special assets from UnitedMake - u(nited)-Boxes.

Owning this NFT package means that you become part of UnitedMake's Community - a membership that grants you access to free artworks airdrops, invites to our VIP events, private tours of our studio and behind the scenes access to our creative projects.

The owners will need to have their package(s) in their wallet at the time of giveaways to redeem the awards.
